title: Dakine Seqouia Glove
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2015 Seqouia Glove.
Features: 
- Insert: Gore Tex® Waterproof / Breathable
- Insulation: High loft synthetic [ Glove 140 / 280g ] [ Mitt 140 / 350g ]
- Lining: 150g Tricot
- Palm: RubberTec palm
- Shell Fabric: Nylon / Poly with DWR treatment
- Removable liner glove: Touch screen compatible 280g 4x4 stretch fleece
- External water resistant zippered stash / heat pack pocket
- One hand cinch gauntlet
- Nose wipe thumb panels
